-dien-bien-phu-den-hoc-sinh-thanh-pho-saint-petersburg-lb-nga-r53648798.epi\" class=\"origin item-origin\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><i class=\"icon inline-block font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-copy text-[13px] mr-[5px]\"></i><span>Gốc</span></a>\n  <i class=\"bm-icon inline-block bg-[url(https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/bm-icon-2.0.3.png)] bg-[length:100px_4250px] align-middle bg-[0_-723px] w-[23px] h-[23px]\"></i>\n </div>\n <h3 class=\"sapo block text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] font-semibold text-[var(--dark)] p-[10px] bg-[#f2f4f5]\">Ng&agrave;y 1.11, Bảo t&agrave;ng Chiến thắng Điện Bi&ecirc;n Phủ phối hợp với Trường THPT Chuy&ecirc;n L&ecirc; Qu&yacute; Đ&ocirc;n tổ chức chương tr&igrave;nh trải nghiệm, giao lưu với Đo&agrave;n c&aacute;n bộ, học sinh th&agrave;nh phố Saint Petersburg, LB Nga.</h3>\n <div class=\"content-body text-[2rem] leading-[2.6rem] text-black mt-[15px] break-words overflow-hidden [&amp;_h1]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h2]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h3]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h4]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_h5]:mb-[15px] [&amp;_p]:mb-[15px] [&amp;&gt;div]:mb-[15px]\">\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:340px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n     <img src=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" alt=\"\" width=\"625\" height=\"340\" />\n    </picture></button>\n  </div>\n  <p class=\"text\">Đ&acirc;y l&agrave; hoạt động &yacute; nghĩa nhằm gi&uacute;p học sinh Việt Nam v&agrave; quốc tế hiểu s&acirc;u sắc hơn tầm v&oacute;c, gi&aacute; trị lịch sử, nh&acirc;n văn của Chiến thắng Điện Bi&ecirc;n Phủ năm 1954 – biểu tượng bất diệt của &yacute; ch&iacute; độc lập, tự do, l&ograve;ng y&ecirc;u nước v&agrave; kh&aacute;t vọng h&ograve;a b&igrave;nh của d&acirc;n tộc Việt Nam.</p>\n  <div class=\"image-wrapper relative z-[1] body-image after:absolute after:top-0 after:left-0 after:z-[-1] after:w-full after:h-full after:opacity-40 after:bg-[url('https://baomoi-static.bmcdn.me/web/styles/img/logo-baomoi-gray.png')] after:bg-[length:20%_auto] after:bg-[position:center_50%] after:bg-no-repeat after:bg-[#e9ecef]\">\n   <i class=\"icon font-['bm-font-icon'] not-italic font-normal normal-case leading-none antialiased [speak:never] [font-variant:normal] ic-search-plus w-[44px] h-[44px] flex items-center justify-center absolute right-[5px] top-[5px] z-[2] text-white rounded-full cursor-pointer bg-[rgba(0,0,0,0.5)] hover:bg-[var(--primary)]\"></i>\n   <button class=\"image lazy-image overflow-hidden photo block leading-[0] cursor-pointer text-center opacity-0\" style=\"width:625px;height:416px\">\n    <picture>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/avif\"></source>\n     <source srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAIAAAP///wAAACH5BAEAAAAALAAAAAABAAEAAAICRAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\"></source>\n  